    "actionItems": [
      "Maintain BMNR cash-secured put ladder but tighten strikes above $62,300 structural level given mixed crypto signals and $2.2B options expiry creating volatility",
      "Prepare to reduce Maturity sector overweight if 10Y approaches 4.50% stress level amid inflation concerns from oil shock",
      "Monitor HYG closely near $80 threshold as credit conditions could deteriorate rapidly if ceasefire talks fail and stagflation materializes"
    ],
    "keySignals": [
      "Oil trading in neutral $97.41-$101.32 range with break above $100 confirming stagflation risk despite ceasefire optimism.",
      "10Y yields steadying ahead of talks but upside inflation pressure building from supply shocks could test 4.50% growth stress level.",
      "VIX regime dynamics critical with ceasefire binary outcome potentially driving sharp volatility compression or spike above 25 line.",
      "Asian stocks posting best week since 2022 while dollar weakens suggests risk-on positioning vulnerable to ceasefire disappointment."
